{
  "stem": "19502.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was-- I went out one time, was 3:00 in the morning,",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "00.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was very cold.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Was already towards the fall.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the-- as I was staying in the line for the bread, just came my turn.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He wouldn't let me in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they took me away, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Job. ?] They took us to do some cleaning at the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There were the horses.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We had to clean up all the dirt.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You know, where the horse had--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They kept the horses in the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They kept the horses in the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The synagogue we were going, [INAUDIBLE] Synagogue.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I didn't-- I didn't mind they already went to work.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I didn't-- I was worried my-- my mother wouldn't know where I was.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But anyway, it was turning dark when they let us go home, so when I came home, she was so happy to see me that-- and then, on top of that, I returned with all the bread.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't give.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You just-- they-- they-- they took-- they just, you know, we didn't have ticket--",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You just line up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We just lined up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they asked-- you wouldn't dare lie.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know what I mean?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If [INAUDIBLE] for how many people?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "For four people.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, you don't dare lie.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But many times they had themselves fun.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We'll stay in a line and a big truck will come in, a German truck.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then a few will get killed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They just run straight into the line, because was a-- but with my father, you see, this was later.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But when my father-- when they came into town, that was in-- that was-- it's in September.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It's a Ukrainian [NON-ENGLISH], it's called.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It's a holiday.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
